<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Jakob Clas</head><p>Der Rat setzt Gerichtstag am Montag vor Antoniustag an und gewährt Geleit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_157" id="77r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l1">Jacob Clas / Als du vns
                            <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haſt / daʒ vvir dir einen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l2">tag ſecʒen ſüllen cʒü <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        rechten / . Alſo beſcheıden vvir dir <add><ab facs="#facs_157_line_1581580037985_73">des </ab></add> einen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l3">tag auf den Montag vor ſant Anthonien tag nu ſchirſt /
                        . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l4">vnd ſolt auch du vnd die mit dir reiten / <del rend="strikethrough">Acht tag bey vns frıd </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l5">
<add>vnſer</add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd </del> geleitt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        / cʒüm rechten vnd da von <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> / .
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r2l6"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ .
                                <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Epıph<ex>aniae</ex></expan> . ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_157" id="77r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Jacob Clas, als du uns <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast, daz wir dir
                        einen tag seczen süllen czü <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten. Also
                        bescheiden wir dir <add>des</add> einen tag auf den <app><note><q type="date">montag vor sant
                            Anthonien tag nu schirst</q>14.01.1409</note></app>; und solt auch du und die mit dir reiten
                            <add>unser</add> geleitt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czüm rechten und
                        da von <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Epiph<ex>aniae</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
